{"tid":2452591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"終於到槍權   奧巴馬︰我們仍忽視了美國槍枝暴力這個長期流行病","createTime":"2021-03-19T02:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T11:41:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"aa706798eab85645986cd44c35d34d5d3d1a23c4","tid":2452591,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:39:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BarackObama/status/1372191746583629827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBarackObama%2Fstatus%2F1372191746583629827&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=79dd176f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBarackObama%2Fstatus%2F1372191746583629827&h=d1901ef8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BarackObama/status/1372191746583629827</a><br />\n<br />\n歐巴馬在推特發布3篇推文，寫道「即便正與新冠疫情奮戰，我們仍忽視了美國槍枝暴力這個長期流行病，雖然槍手的動機尚不明瞭，但受害者的身分彰顯了一件事實，那就是對亞裔持續升高的暴力行徑必須被終結。」<br />\n<br />\n歐巴馬的另一則推文說，「槍擊事件提醒了我們，在槍枝安全立法及根除社會仇恨、暴力的工作上，我們離取得共識還有一大段路要走。」歐巴馬提到，他和夫人蜜雪兒為受害者及其家庭祈禱，強調所有人都對這起毫無必要的殺傷事件感到悲痛，敦促當局採取有效行動保障大眾生命安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3471063\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3471063&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=d842fe7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3471063&h=85f4575d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3471063</a>"},{"pid":"2c32df995c79bf27ab6acf9779846579084a8f61","tid":2452591,"uid":54681,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:42:12.000Z","msg":"食屎啦黑力架"},{"pid":"316188244645425f1f9a56f30713b5080ede4e09","tid":2452591,"uid":34410,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixAk4Xu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: